Kad apmeklētājs noklikšķina uz banera, informācija par to tiek saglabāta sīkdatnē (cookies). Ja apmeklētājs vēlāk uziet uz kāda cita referāļa banera, sistēma var pārrakstīt šo sīkdatni vai arī nē.
Ja sīkdatne tiek pārrakstīta, tad komisiju saņem pēdējais referālis, uz kura banera bija klikšķinājis apmeklētājs. 
Ja tas netiek pārrakstīts, pirmais referālis saņem komisiju.

Ja uzstādīts, sistēma sistēma dzēš sīkdatni pēc pārdošanas/piesaistes transakcijas. Tas nozīmē, ka partneris nesaņems komisijas par vēlākajiem šī apakšpartnera pirkumiem.
Pēc noklusējuma, sīkdatne netiek izdzēsta un partneris saņem komisijas par visiem nākotnes maksājumiem, kurus veic apakšpartneris.

Ja neviens partneris nav atsūtījis konkrēto pārdošanu/piesaisti, komisija tiek saglabāta "noklusējuma" partnerim, kas izvēlēts zemāk.
Šo var izmantot, lai izsekotu visām pārdošanām, ne tikai tām, kuras piesaistīja afilātes.

translation:
Šis pirmais solis ir ļoti nozīmīgs - padomājiet par savu partneru programmu.
Jums jābūt plānam, ko jūs ar to vēlaties sasniegt. Cik daudz jūs varat atļauties izmaksāt komisijās?
Vai tās būs pietiekoši pievilcīgas, salīdzinot ar jūsu konkurentiem? Kā veicināt partneru piesaisti?

Viena vadošā kampaņa tiek izveidota instalācijas laikā. Jūs varat to modificēt vai radīt jaunas kampaņas.

Kampaņas tiek izmantotas, lai grupētu produktu grupas (vai vienu produktu) kam ir identiski komisiju iestatījumi.

Piemēram, jums var būt kampaņa Produktam1, kur jūs atalgojat partnerus par klikšķi, un cita kampaņa Produktam2, kur partneri saņem komisijas par pārdošanām.

Vai arī, jums var būt kampaņa, kas saucas Zemo izmaksu produkti, kur jūs izmaksājat 40% no pārdošanas komisijās, un cita kampaņa, kas saucas Dārgo izmaksu produkti ar 15% par pārdošanu komisijās.

Baneru pārvaldniekājūs atradīsiet dažādu veidu banerus, sākot ar teksta saitēm, standarta baneriem, kā arī HTML, Flash un reklāmas e-pastu baneriem.
Katram banerim jābūt savam URL - kurp tiks novirzīts apmeklētājs, kad tas uzies uz baneri.
Pielāgojiet savām vajadzībām partneru reģistrācijas formu

Izvērtējiet standarta reģistrācijas veidlapu, un pielāgojiet to, ja tas nepieciešams.

Reģistrācijas veidlapa tiek aprīkota ar mini-tīmekļa vietni, kura satur informāciju par partneru programmu utt.
Jūs varat izmantot mini-tīmekļa vietni, vai arī izdzēst to un izmantot tikai reģistrācijas veidlapu.

source:
Integration is a way to connect the affiliate system to your current website, shopping cart or payment gateway in a way that affiliate system will be notified about referrals and purchases.
When notified, affiliate system registers the sale, finds referring affiliate (if any) and creates appropriate commission for him.

Integration usually means adding few lines of code into your pages, and it is described step-by-step in the Integration guide for most common shopping carts and payment systems.%s
translation:
Integrācija ir veids, kādā partneru sistēma pieslēdzas jūsu patreizējai tīmekļa vietnei, pirkumu grozam vai maksājumu procesoram tā, lai afilāšu sistēma tiktu informēta par reģistrācijām un pirkumiem.
Kad saņem ziņu, partnerprogramma reģistrē pārdošanu, atrod partneri (ja tāds ir), kurš atbildīgs par pārdošanu un izveido attiecīgu komisiju viņam.

Integrācija parasti nozīmē to, ka kodam jūsu lapās tiek pievienotas daļas rindas, un tas tiek aprakstīts soli pa solim Integrācijas instrukcijā, kur minētas plašāk pazīstamās maksājumu sistēmas un iepirkumu grozi.%s

source:
When you have configured your campaigns, defined correct commissions, and created some banners/links, you should test the system.
The best is to simulate the whole process from affiliate’s and your point of view:
  1. Sign up as some testing affiliate – after approval you should receive confirmation email with your password, and you should be able to log in to your affiliate panel
  2. Log in to affiliates panel, get the code for banners/links and put them onto some testing page
  3. Click on the banner and check that the click is registered
  4. After the click, try to make test sale and check that sale commission was registered in affiliate system (only for per sale or per lead commissions)
If you experience some problems in any of these steps, turn on Debug event logging and look at Troubleshooting%s
translation:
Kad esat nokonfigurējis kampaņas, komisijas un izvedojis banerus/saites, jums vajadzētu notestēt sistēmu.
Vislabākais ir simulēt visu procesu no partnera un sava redzes punkta:
  1. Piereģistrējieties, kā testa affiliate - pēc reģistrācijas jums vajadzētu saņemt apstiprnājuma e-pastu ar jūsu paroli, un jums būtu jāienāk sistēmā
  2. Ienākot sistēmā, izvēlieties kādu no baneriem/saitēm un izvietojiet tos kādā no testa lapām.
  3. Spiediet uz baneri un pārliecinieties, ka klikšļis ir reģistrēts
  4. Pēc klikšķa pamēģiniet veikt testa pārdošanu un pārliecinieties, ka pārdošanas komisija ir tikusi reģistrēta sistēmā (tas attiecas tikai uz pārdošanas vai piesaistīšanas komisijâm)
Ja jums rodas kādas problēmas kādā no soļiem, aktivizējietDebug event logging un meklējietKļūdas iemeslu%s

Kad esat pabeidzis(usi) izmēģināt afilāšu sistēmas integrāciju jūsu tīmekļa vietnē, viss ir gatavs, lai sāktu reklamēt savu jauno afilāšu programmu, lai piesaistītu jaunus partnerus.

Obligāti neaizmirstiet pievienot saiti uz savu partnerprogrammas informāciju vai reģistrācijas formu savā mājas lapā. Nosauciet saiti Partnerprogramma vai tamlīdzīgi. Tas piesaistīs lietotājus jūsu tīmekļa vietnei, kuri vēlāk var kļūt par jūsu partneriem.

Lai sasniegtu vairāk potenciālos partnerus, iesniedziet savu programmu specializētās partneru direktorijās. Internetā ir vairāki desmiti partneru direktoriju, kuras apmeklē tūkstoši pieredzējušu partneru katru dienu.

source: Weekly report is sent every week with the statistics of the week's traffic and sales. It is sent on the day specified in "report sent on" and contains data from the previous complete week. The first day of week can be specified in "week starts at".
translation: Nedēļas atskaite tiek sūtīta katru dienu ar statistiku par dienas trafiku un pārdošanām. Tā tiek nosūtīta dienā, kas noteikta "atskaite nosītīta"un satur datus par visu pagājušo nedēļu. Pirmā nedēļas diena var tikt noteikta "nedēļa sākas ar".

source: Monthly report is sent every month with the statistics of the month's traffic and sales. It is sent on a day specified in "report sent on" and contains data from previous month. e.g. If "report sent on" is set to 31 and month has only 30 days, then the report is sent on the last day of the month. It is recommended that you set "report sent on" to one of the first days of month, so that data in report is current.
translation: Mēneša atskaite tiek sūtīta katru dienu ar statistiku par dienas trafiku un pārdošanām. Tā tiek nosūtīta dienā, kas specificēta "atskaite nosūtīta"un satur datus par pagājušo mēnesi, piemēram, ja "atskaite nosūtīta" ir iestatīta uz 31 un mēnesī ir tikai 30 dienas, tad atskaite tiek nosūtīta mēneša pēdējā dienā. Ir ieteicams, lai jūs iestatāt "atskaite nosūtīta" vienā no pirmajām mēneša dienām, lai atskaišu datums ir patreizējais.

Post Affiliate Xpress is made in a way that it can work with the default configuration.
However, you should check the configuration and fine tune it for your own needs.
You can find the configuration screen under the Config & Tools menu -> Configuration.

The detailed description of all configuration options can be found in the user's guide or knowledgebase.

You should set up emailing functionality. This includes:
  • mail account - how the emails are sent. You can choose either mail() function or SMTP server.
  • email templates – these are templates that are used when system sends automatic emails, like after signup or after sale notifications
  • email notifications – you can configure what kind of notifications you would like to receive as merchant, and what notifications will be available for affiliates.
Make sure that mail account is set up properly – try to test sending emails. Without working emails the affiliates will not receive confirmation about their signups, etc.

Affiliate panel in Post Affiliate Xpress is very flexible.
You can configure how the menu will look like, what content you want to have there, and even write your own content or link to another pages.
Below you can see tasks waiting for your approval and the overview of the affiliate program traffic

They can help you troubleshoot problems with tracking, just turn on error logging and you'll see every action of the system.

translation:
GeoIp Core module will translate every Ip address into Location (Country, City, Latitude and Longitude).
All other GeoIp functionality is based on this plugin.
If this plugin will not be enabled, other GeoIp plugins will not work too.
Please read more how to configure plugin correctly in section "More info".

source:
GeoIp plugin is based on free GeoIp database offered by MaxMind.
Plugin requires GeoIp binary database (filename GeoLiteCity.dat) saved in your plugin directory (server/plugins/GeoIp/).
You can downlaod latest version of GeoIp database from here: %s.
(Don't forget to extract downloaded file before copying to plugin directory)
Free GeoIp database has lower accuracy as paid version offered by MaxMind, but for most of installations it will be enough, because in most cases you are interested in country level information and City level is not so important.
If you want to have more accurate results of IP identification, you will need to buy GeoCity library from %s and replace file GeoLiteCity.dat in your plugin directory with one you received from MaxMind.
Accuracy of Free GeoIp database: Over 99.3%% on a country level and 76%% on a city level for the US within a 25 mile radius.
Accuracy of Paid GeoIp database: Over 99.8%% on a country level and 81%% on a city level for the US within a 25 mile radius.
translation:
GeoIp plugin is based on free GeoIp database offered by MaxMind.
Plugin requires GeoIp binary database (filename GeoLiteCity.dat) saved in your plugin directory (server/plugins/GeoIp/).
You can downlaod latest version of GeoIp database from here: %s.
(Don't forget to extract downloaded file before copying to plugin directory)
Free GeoIp database has lower accuracy as paid version offered by MaxMind, but for most of installations it will be enough, because in most cases you are interested in country level information and City level is not so important.
If you want to have more accurate results of IP identification, you will need to buy GeoCity library from %s and replace file GeoLiteCity.dat in your plugin directory with one you received from MaxMind.
Accuracy of Free GeoIp database: Over 99.3%% on a country level and 76%% on a city level for the US within a 25 mile radius.
Accuracy of Paid GeoIp database: Over 99.8%% on a country level and 81%% on a city level for the US within a 25 mile radius.

source: This is a formula based on which all the commissions will be counted. If main commission structure should be set to 1st tier 5%; 2nd tier 4% and 3rd tier 3% the formula would look like %3-%4-%5. In case you want to payout flat commission, the formula requires only numbers: 3-4-5. This structure defines tiers from right to left, meaning the first one from left is top tier, then their child, then grandchild etc...
translation: This is a formula based on which all the commissions will be counted. If main commission structure should be set to 1st tier 5%; 2nd tier 4% and 3rd tier 3% the formula would look like %3-%4-%5. In case you want to payout flat commission, the formula requires only numbers: 3-4-5. This structure defines tiers from right to left, meaning the first one from left is top tier, then their child, then grandchild etc...

source:
If main commission structure should be set to 1st tier 5%; 2nd tier 4% and 3rd tier 3% the formula would look like %3-%4-%5. In case you want to payout flat commission, the formula requires only numbers: 3-4-5. This structure defines tiers from right to left, meaning the first one from left is top tier, then their child, then grandchild etc... The missing tier commission always goes to the parent affiliate (from right to left).

E.g. in case of five levels %2-%2-%2-%4-%5 the commission structure changes like this, if the last affiliate is missing:
All 5 tiers: %2-%2-%2-%4-%5
4 tiers: %2-%2-%2-%9
3 tiers: %2-%2-%11
2 tiers: %2-%13
1 tier: %15
translation:
If main commission structure should be set to 1st tier 5%; 2nd tier 4% and 3rd tier 3% the formula would look like %3-%4-%5. In case you want to payout flat commission, the formula requires only numbers: 3-4-5. This structure defines tiers from right to left, meaning the first one from left is top tier, then their child, then grandchild etc... The missing tier commission always goes to the parent affiliate (from right to left).

E.g. in case of five levels %2-%2-%2-%4-%5 the commission structure changes like this, if the last affiliate is missing:
All 5 tiers: %2-%2-%2-%4-%5
4 tiers: %2-%2-%2-%9
3 tiers: %2-%2-%11
2 tiers: %2-%13
1 tier: %15

source:
The last affiliate tier with no parent in a sale will get the commission as a difference between the totalcost and the sum of commissions given to lower tiers.
Notice: Use this plugin only in case you want to pay all the totalcost (100% commission) to your affiliates.
translation:
The last affiliate tier with no parent in a sale will get the commission as a difference between the totalcost and the sum of commissions given to lower tiers.
Notice: Use this plugin only in case you want to pay all the totalcost (100% commission) to your affiliates.

source:
Example 1:
Let's have the main commission structure set like this: 1st tier 50%; 2nd tier 30% and 3rd tier 20%. Now here are some cases:
  • Commission for all 3 tiers: Every tier gets the commission noramlly (50%, 30%, 20%)
  • Commission for 2 tiers: The 1st tier gets 50% and the 2nd tier gets 'totalcost' - 50%(lower tiers)
  • Commission for 1 tier: The 1st tier gets commission of 'totalcost' - 0(there is no lower tier) = 100%
Example 2:
Let's have the main commission structure set like this: 1st tier 30%; 2nd tier 20% and 3rd tier 10%, for all tiers the commission is 60%. Now here are some cases:
  • Commission for all 3 tiers: Every tier gets the commission noramlly (30%, 20%, 10%)
  • Commission for 2 tiers: The 1st tier gets 30% and the 2nd tier gets 'totalcost' - 30%(lower tiers) = 70%, for all tiers the commission is 100%!
  • Commission for 1 tier: The 1st tier gets commission of 'totalcost' - 0(there is no lower tier), so for all tiers the commission is 100%!
translation:
Example 1:
Let's have the main commission structure set like this: 1st tier 50%; 2nd tier 30% and 3rd tier 20%. Now here are some cases:
  • Commission for all 3 tiers: Every tier gets the commission noramlly (50%, 30%, 20%)
  • Commission for 2 tiers: The 1st tier gets 50% and the 2nd tier gets 'totalcost' - 50%(lower tiers)
  • Commission for 1 tier: The 1st tier gets commission of 'totalcost' - 0(there is no lower tier) = 100%
Example 2:
Let's have the main commission structure set like this: 1st tier 30%; 2nd tier 20% and 3rd tier 10%, for all tiers the commission is 60%. Now here are some cases:
  • Commission for all 3 tiers: Every tier gets the commission noramlly (30%, 20%, 10%)
  • Commission for 2 tiers: The 1st tier gets 30% and the 2nd tier gets 'totalcost' - 30%(lower tiers) = 70%, for all tiers the commission is 100%!
  • Commission for 1 tier: The 1st tier gets commission of 'totalcost' - 0(there is no lower tier), so for all tiers the commission is 100%!
